cluster_relations.rel_desc: The Arab Spring started in the year 2010.
cluster_relations.canonical_rel_desc: Indicates the time point or time period when an event, process, or described history begins.

cluster_relations.rel_desc: The human spirit is described as having the power to create a better world.
cluster_relations.canonical_rel_desc: Indicates that the subject exerts a non-exclusive causal or enabling influence that helps bring about the object event, state, or outcome.

args.canonical_rel_desc: Indicates the specific time point or time period at which an event, process, or historical episode begins.
args.justification: Refines the canonical predicate from 'starts_in_time' to 'starts_at_time' for clearer, more standard temporal phrasing while preserving the same onset semantics; the existing class and group correctly capture an event-beginning temporal relation and are retained.
